#. Possible error message when a site presents a bad certificate.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1786
msgid ""
"This website presented identification that belongs to a different website."
msgstr "ເວັບໄຊນີ້ສະແດງຕົວຕົນທີ່ເປັນຂອງເວັບໄຊອື່ນ."

#. Possible error message when a site presents a bad certificate.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1791
msgid ""
"This website’s identification is too old to trust. Check the date on your "
"computer’s calendar."
msgstr "ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງເວັບໄຊນີ້ເກົ່າເກີນໄປທີ່ຈະເຊື່ອຖືໄດ້. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບວັນທີໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານ."

#. Possible error message when a site presents a bad certificate.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1796
msgid "This website’s identification was not issued by a trusted organization."
msgstr "ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງເວັບໄຊນີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກອອກໂດຍອົງກອນທີ່ເຊື່ອຖືໄດ້."

#. Possible error message when a site presents a bad certificate.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1801
msgid ""
"This website’s identification could not be processed. It may be corrupted."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດປະມວນຜົນການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງເວັບໄຊນີ້ໄດ້. ມັນອາດຈະເສຍຫາຍ."

#. Possible error message when a site presents a bad certificate.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1806
msgid ""
"This website’s identification has been revoked by the trusted organization "
"that issued it."
msgstr "ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງເວັບໄຊນີ້ຖືກຍົກເລີກໂດຍອົງກອນທີ່ອອກໃຫ້."

#. Possible error message when a site presents a bad certificate.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1811
msgid ""
"This website’s identification cannot be trusted because it uses very weak "
"encryption."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເຊື່ອຖືການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງເວັບໄຊນີ້ໄດ້ ເນື່ອງຈາກມັນໃຊ້ການເຂົ້າລະຫັດທີ່ອ່ອນແອຫຼາຍ."

#. Possible error message when a site presents a bad certificate.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1816
msgid ""
"This website’s identification is only valid for future dates. Check the date "
"on your computer’s calendar."
msgstr "ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງເວັບໄຊນີ້ຈະມີຜົນໃນອະນາຄົດເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບວັນທີໃນຄອມພິວເຕີຂອງທ່ານ."

#. Page title when a site cannot be loaded due to a network error.
#. Page title when a site cannot be loaded due to a page crash error.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1881 embed/ephy-web-view.c:1937
#, c-format
msgid "Problem Loading Page"
msgstr "ມີບັນຫາໃນການໂຫຼດໜ້າເວັບ"

#. Message title when a site cannot be loaded due to a network error.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1884
msgid "Unable to display this website"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດສະແດງເວັບໄຊນີ້ໄດ້"

#. Error details when a site cannot be loaded due to a network error.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1889
#, c-format
msgid "The site at %s seems to be unavailable."
msgstr "ເວັບໄຊທີ່ %s ເບິ່ງຄືວ່າບໍ່ພ້ອມໃຊ້ງານ."

#. Further error details when a site cannot be loaded due to a network error.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1893
msgid ""
"It may be temporarily inaccessible or moved to a new address. You may wish "
"to verify that your internet connection is working correctly."
msgstr "ມັນອາດຈະເຂົ້າເຖິງບໍ່ໄດ້ຊົ່ວຄາວ ຫຼື ຍ້າຍໄປທີ່ຢູ່ໃໝ່. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບວ່າການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ອິນເຕີເນັດຂອງທ່ານເຮັດວຽກປົກກະຕິຫຼືບໍ່."

#. Technical details when a site cannot be loaded due to a network error.
#: embed/ephy-web-view.c:1903
#, c-format
msgid "The precise error was: %s"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດທີ່ລະບຸຄື: %s"

